column5: I’m sorry to hear that you feel its ur only solution, sometimes it can seem like the truth. I hear this all the time and im so fucking tired of it, but even tho one has unsolvable problems, they can still live a good life <3
I don’t because i end up disappointing myself :|
Your therapist will only tell your parents if they think your life is in immediate danger hope u figure it out uwu
I love it because then i get a reason to kill myself lol
